In what will come across as a really shocking development, a final year student of the Obafemi Awolowo university has been killed. Ebenezer Chiwendu Linda It has been reported that a final year Accounting student of the Obafemi Awolowo University, Ile Ife, Osun State, has died. Local reports show that the lady who was identified as Ebenezer Chiwendu Linda, died after being hit by a trailer, following a brake failure. Ebenezer Chiwendu Linda who is also known as Wendy, was reportedly hit at the busy Mayfair bus stop, on Monday evening. The student, who was at the last stage of ICAN, was later confirmed dead at the Obafemi Awolowo University Teaching University. The sad incident has left many students really devastated. Source